Package: EnergyAnalytics
Title: Data Foundation and Dashboard UI for Energy Analytics
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(
      given = "Brandon",
      family = "Choi",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      email = "brandonchoi@users.noreply.github.com"
    )
Description: Creates and loads local, versioned calculation datasets for the
    EnergyAnalytics project and provides the UI shell for a production-style
    Golem dashboard. Source data is normalized into canonical Feather datasets
    for downstream calculations. The dashboard is wired to the local snapshot
    using dedicated calculation engines for each module, ensuring the app never
    calls external APIs at runtime.
